-- Mets Put Pitcher Mike Pelfrey on Disabled List With Elbow Injury
-- B y   M i c h a e l   S i l l u p
-- 2012-04-24T21:11:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-24/mets-put-pitcher-mike-pelfrey-on-disabled-list-with-elbow-injury.html
The New York Mets put pitcher  Mike
Pelfrey  on the disabled list with swelling in his right elbow,
the team said in a press release.  Pelfrey, who started three games without getting a
decision, had a 2.29 earned run average this season. Pelfrey is
still awaiting a final diagnosis of the injury.  The Mets also placed outfielder Jason Bay on the disabled
list today with a broken rib.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Sillup at 
 msillup@bloomberg.net  